  "subject": "Hibernate validation test",
  "commit_message": "Hibernate validation test\n\nThis adds a test where Hibernate validation is enabled.\nThis will detect mismatches between database schema and JPA\nentity definitions. For example, if a new field is added in\nJava but not in Liquibase, the test fails with an error:\n\n  missing column [restarting] in table [AutomationComposition]\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5401\nChange-Id: Ieb718353ff1cdff0dd92415743aefc56d838b1e6\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\n",
